title: Mounds Brownies
directions: As soon as you take the brownies from the oven, spread the coconut/milk mixture over hot brownies.
1 container chocolate frosting..microwaved just longer enough to make the frosting pourable. Pour over the brownies topped with coconut mixture. Spread to seal edges.
ingredients: 1 brownie mix (9x13 size)...mixed and baked according to box directions.
Mix the coconut and milk together.
